A lot of twists and deaths. I feel like: Stuffed full of too many bags\, too many cute little creatures\, and not enough REAL stakes. There were few twists\, few turns\, and few surprises (although the ones that were there were truly surprising)\, and a large portion of the movie was focused on two inconsequential characters doing something inconsequential to the rest of the story. I was expecting the excitement of Rogue One. Did not get it.
